FindJpegTurbo.cmake = custom macro to find the jpeg-turbo library
options_cmake.h.in = CMake compilation time header were variables can be added
utils.cmake = common CMake functions used in the program, mostly compilation flags
/linux = some files needed to create Linux packages
/mac = some files needed to create MAC packages
/win = some files needed to create Win32 packages (the DLLs for OpenSSL downloaded from https://code.google.com/p/openssl-for-windows/)
/win64 = some files needed to create Win64 packages (the DDLs for OpenSSL downloaded from https://code.google.com/p/openssl-for-windows/)

